<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="J" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Jot" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Jot,</orth> a point, a tittle, the least quantity imaginable: <cit><quote>if springing things be any j. diminished,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 417" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 417</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if you break one j. of your promise,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.194" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 194</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if one j. beyond the bound of honour,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 51</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>brings a thousand-fold more care to keep than in possession any j. of pleasure,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 53</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if this salute my blood a j.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.103" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 103</bibl></cit>. Mostly with a negative: <bibl n="shak. mm 4.2.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 2, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.128" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.306" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 306</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.241" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 241</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 2, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.363" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 363</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.217" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 217</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 1, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.2.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 2, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.126" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 126</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 122</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.215" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 215</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.5.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 5, 13</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>